<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Booking Confirmed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .details { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .otp-box { 
            background-color: #e8eaf6; padding: 15px; text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px dashed #3f51b5;
        }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Booking Confirmed</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Respected Pandit Ji,</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for accepting the booking for <strong><%= poojaName %></strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="details">
                <h3>Booking Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= time %></p>
                <p><strong>Devotee Name:</strong> <%= userName %></p>
                <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= userPhone %></p>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> <%= userAddress %></p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Verification OTP:</h3>
            <div class="otp-box">
                <%= otp %>
            </div>
            <p>Please collect this OTP from the devotee when you arrive to verify the booking.</p>
            
            <p>We appreciate your service to the community.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Vaidic Parampara. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>